import React from 'react' const MainBoard = props => { return(
  • Date: {new Date(props.day.dt * 1000).toDateString()}
  • Sunrise: {props.day.sunrise}
  • Sunset: {props.day.sunset}
  • Temp:
    • day: {props.day.temp.day}
    • min: {props.day.temp.min}
    • max: {props.day.temp.max}
    • night: {props.day.temp.night}
    • eve: {props.day.temp.eve}
    • morn: {props.day.temp.morn}
  • Pressure: {props.day.pressure}
  • Humidity: {props.day.humidity}
  • Wind speed: {props.day.wind_speed}
) } export default MainBoard
